This is a DAQ (Data AcQuisition) module for Snort 3. It links against and is a
derivative work of libdaq (https://github.com/snort3/libdaq), which is licensed
under the GNU General Public License, version 2. Accordingly, this module is
licensed under the GNU General Public License, version 2 (GPL-2.0-only), as
stated in the header of every source file in this directory and in the LICENSE /
COPYING files here.

It bridges Snort 3 to the FD.io VPP data plane over a shared-memory Unix socket
(see daq_vpp_shared.h). Project: https://github.com/snort3 ; https://fd.io/
